Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a captain at Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not live on in disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop you guys\Nby slashing you in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow that…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as our destination lies\Nbeyond where you stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate crooked sword attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right-Angle Flying Bird…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…Bone…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He discerned it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:01:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bold Hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He defeated Ship-Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he\Nfollowed the sea train
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the detached cars\Nin this storm…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your justice is deep, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we also shoulder\Nall sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiss! You're the very definition\Nof "all bark but no bite."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you guys being\Ndeceived by that woman, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the lowest of the low,\Nwho lived one betrayal after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and survived until today\Nin the underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decoupage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you add your last\Nwords to them while you're at it, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where on earth\Ndid you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:03:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish taking\Ncare of the ramen guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did, just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's suddenly become noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the soldiers for this escort mission\Nwere annihilated after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't expect much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who\Nkidnapped Robin-chan, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They use strange martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably that CP9 newbie\Nthat Corgy was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's a Four Power\NMaster named Nero or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call me a fighting genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care anymore…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y… You must be Rob Lucci, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that I didn't\Nintroduce myself sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him first and…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're capturing Franky alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you let your feelings take\Ncontrol and lost sight of our mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run…? From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What…? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Don't be foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:51.22,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now\Nlet's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:54.64,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:58.02,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through\Nour clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:06.04,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:13.05,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Working together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:16.78,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:20.19,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:23.96,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,there's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:27.61,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:30.92,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:34.39,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through\Nthe rainbow-colored wind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:38.06,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:41.71,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey\Nfraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:45.74,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most\Nwill be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:49.40,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:52.45,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:56.62,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right!\NNow let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:06:00.16,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:03.54,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:07.67,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:11.38,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up\Nthe pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.68,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map\Nleading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:18.10,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:23.45,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag--\Ntogether, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:31.47,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Scramble over Robin!\NA Cunning Plan by Sogeking!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run…? From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What…? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Don't be foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person like you who does\Neverything halfway
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is unfit for CP9!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you've mastered all Six Powers,\Nyou aren't superhuman, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalifa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inform our chief later…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the newbie was so\Nweak that he was useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are supposed\Nto be working for justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:08:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't tell which side is evil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Officials from the World\NGovernment sure are ill-mannered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my duty, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sense of smell\Nis absolute, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take off that cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Now! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W… Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sogeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man\Nwho hails from the island of snipers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can\Nget away with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the resolution\Nof a man who is willing to go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L… L… Lucci-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have to ask\Nwhy you are here, intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the way you opened the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't seem like\Nyou have a lot of patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm ill-bred, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is about Nico Robin…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too big of an issue for you\Nguys to get yourselves involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people in the world who\Nwere born under an unlucky star...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who are better off\Ndead for everyone's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suppose there exists a devil that\Nwould burn the world to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:10:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the person who\Ncan raise this devil
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is an innocent girl\Nwho's only eight years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…don't you think…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…that someone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should kill\Nthis girl for everyone's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you\Nthat is Nico Robin's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a real criminal now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it started simple like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since she can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her existence itself was a sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can make others happy\Nonly by disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the misfortune she carries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Essentially,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she should've died 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad that this\Nwoman will be put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the Government\Nwill probably spend years...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…squeezing out all\Nof Nico Robin's knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,experience and intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much agony she'll experience\Nbefore she dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you just watch and--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, wait, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Seriously! Seriously! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't good…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to all the trouble\Nof getting in from outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even brought\Nthat official down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She indeed bears a resemblance to\Nthe picture in the wanted poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back together this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring these guys down\Nright away, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I explain, you guys\Njust won't get it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I explain, you guys\Njust won't get it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detach car #3!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One moment will decide the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Franky get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke… Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a petty thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he said we're turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we should get\Nready to turn back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! When we came this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Robin!\NWhat about Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're we gonna do\Nabout them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that guy thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we turning back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us why!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was telling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that frog that jumped\Non the railway to turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit! Ribbit! Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yokozuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokozuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that huge frog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step aside, frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna collide!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got Robin back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,\Nthat sure surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that we suddenly switched\Nto a "Running Away" strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A smoke screen is so stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that people wouldn't normally\Nthink of using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we can achieve our goal\Nwithout fighting scary guys like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't know if things\Nare gonna be that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down\Nuntil the cars are really far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thorny whips?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught it…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:17:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he gonna use the whips\Nto cross over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They pulled us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A smoke screen?\NWhat a worthless thing to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it couldn't\Nhave worked after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill any Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Robin-chan\Nat all costs, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm…? Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm going to…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…make you let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is his body so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that they use\Nstrange martial arts, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:18:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concasser!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got quite a heavy kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body almost got broken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blueno, don't take him lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have a bounty on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's one of their main forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just noticed that,\Nyou damn jerks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, R-Robin!\NHey, hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow… Wh-What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocho Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long-nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why, Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times\Ndo I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez… Why are all of you\Nbeing so stubborn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even towards your friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a perfect chance to run, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't expect that, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you taking sides\Nwith them in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't bear to watch\Nthose guys act like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not when there's a team that couldn't\Ngo back even if they wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've joined up with Straw Hat,\Nget back to town somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting\Nlike that at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to rescue you\Nknowing all the circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we just do something about the\NGovernment's attack, Buster Call,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there shouldn't be a reason that\Nyou have to obey them, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Buster Call is…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…indeed the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:09.38,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:14.20,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:19.23,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,makes us able to cross
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:23.23,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:30.07,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,You're braver and more caring
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.09,0:22:32.78,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:38.09,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever depart this ship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:42.79,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.81,0:22:45.68,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:53.70,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Let Robin-chan go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!\NWhy aren't you saying anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.14,0:23:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, you're still hiding\Nsomething, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.29,0:23:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a pirate cannot leave their group\Nwithout their captain's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Robin…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,believe in Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Judicial Island!\NFull View of Enies Lobby!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
